Class DrinkDisplay

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Panel
          • sg.edu.nus.iss.vmcs.maintenance.DrinkDisplay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class DrinkDisplay
extends java.awt.Panel
    This interface object is part of the MaintenancePanel. It is used by the Maintainer to display the total number of cans of each DrinksBrand that are currently held in the DrinksStore. This object contains buttons which represent (and to select) the DrinksBrand served by the vending machine.
    Version:
    3.0 5/07/2003
    Author:
    Olivo Miotto, Pang Ping Li
